🛠️ How to Run the Laptop Booking Server (Step-by-Step)
📁 1. Prerequisites
Before running the server, make sure the following are installed:

Node.js (v14+)

npm (comes with Node.js)

Postman

📂 2. Open The Project With Visual Studio Code

📂 3. Install Required Packages
In the terminal, go to your project directory and run:

npm init -y
npm install express body-parser jsonwebtoken bcryptjs cors fs-extra crypto express-rate-limit

▶️ 4. Run the Server
Run this command:

node server.js
You should see:

✅ Laptop booking server running at http://localhost:3000
